 pale complexion)."],"variants":[]},{"name":"ferch","type":"LAST","attribution":"Dictionary of American Family Names © Patrick Hanks 2003, 2006.","meanings":["German: variant of   Ferg  . Compare   Verch  .","Probably also an Americanized form of German <b>Förtsch</b> (see   Foertsch  ).","Probably also an Americanized form of German <b>Förch</b> (see   Foerch  )."],"variants":[{"name":"Ferg","meanings":["1  ‘Sharp blade’.","2  ‘Wind’."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Gwenllian ferch Llywelyn was born about 1414, in Llangurig, Montgomeryshire, Wales, United Kingdom, her father, Llywelyn ap Philip, was 28 and her mother, Mrs. Llywelyn ap Philip, was 24. She had at least 3 sons and 2 daughters with Rhys Goch ap Llywelyn."},"et":{"ABT    1414–":"umbes 1414–Surnud","1414–Female":"1414–Surnud","1396–1457":"1396–1457","1410–Male":"1410–Surnud","1430–Female":"1430–Surnud","1427–Male":"1427–Surnud","1440–Male":"1440–Surnud","1451–Male":"1451–Surnud","–Female":"Surnud","1388–Male":"1388–Surnud","1392–Female":"1392–Surnud","1440":"1440","1451":"1451","1396":"1396","1392":"1392","ABT    1414":"umbes 1414","1414":"1414","1457":"1457","about 1427":"umbes 1427","1388":"1388","1410":"1410","1430":"1430","about 1451":"umbes 1451","about 1430":"umbes 1430","1427":"1427","Gwlad Morgan, Wales":"Glamorgan, Wales","of Cefnhafodau,Llangurig,Montgomeryshire,Wales":"Llangurig, Montgomeryshire, Wales, United Kingdom","of,Cantref Mawr,Breconshire,Wales":"Cantref, Breconshire, Wales, United Kingdom","Llangristiolus,Malltraeth,Anglesey,Wales":"Llangristiolus, Gwynedd, Wales, United Kingdom","{Tudur Trefor}":"Trevor, Llangollen, Clwyd, Wales, United Kingdom","Gwlad, Carmarthenshire, Wales":"Gwlad, Carmarthenshire, Wales"},"fi":{"ABT    1414–":"noin 1414–Kuollut","1414–Female":"1414–Kuollut","1396–1457":"1396–1457","1410–Male":"1410–Kuollut","1430–Female":"1430–Kuollut","1427–Male":"1427–Kuollut","1440–Male":"1440–Kuollut","1451–Male":"1451–Kuollut","–Female":"Kuollut","1388–Male":"1388–Kuollut","1392–